40px;max-width: 1000px;background-image: url('https://sdqa.vpanel.shakedeal.com/assets/dabf0992-add0-41b7-87ba-03122f83ffa9');background-size: cover;background-position: center center;background-repeat: no-repeat;margin: 0 auto;\">\n <tbody>\n <tr><th style=\"width: 736px;display: flex;\">\n <img style=\"width: 146px;height: 35px;padding-top: 15px;padding-bottom: 15px;padding-left: 50px;\n \" alt=\"Logo\" src=\"https://sdqa.shakedeal.com/images/logos/2/ShakeDealLogo.png\">\n <p style=\"font-weight: 600;font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;font-size: 13px;color: #3e3e3e;padding-left: 16px;\n padding-top: 15px;\n \"> </p>\n </th>\n </tr><tr>\n <td style=\"padding-left: 50px;font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\">\n <div style=\"width: 641px;background-color: #fff!important;color:#000!important;height: 700px;border-radius: 14px;margin-bottom:33px;font-size: 11px;\">\n <p style=\"padding-left: 34px;text-align: left; padding-top:31px;\">Dear Sir/Madam,</p>\n \n <p style=\" padding-left: 35px;text-align: justify; padding-top:5px;width: 545px; line-height: 20px\">We’re pleased to award our Purchase order <strong>SDNKES7100035494-10</strong>for the supply of mentioned material to <strong>NKES &nbsp;</strong>Plant,<strong> Vedanta Limited.</strong></p>\n \n <p style=\"height: 20px; padding-left: 35px;text-align: justify;width: 545px;line-height: 20px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;\">Please log in to our <a style=\"font-size: 11px;color: #282525;\" href=\"https://demo.vpanel.shakedeal.com/admin\"><strong>vendor panel </strong></a>using the button below to review the details and acknowledge your acceptance of the PO on the panel.</span> </p>\n \n<p style=\"background-color: #d5b568; color: #fff;padding: 6px 10px; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 21px; display: inline-block;padding-right: 14px;font-weight: 600;\"><a href=\"{{po_link}}\" style=\"color:#fff;font-family: 'Montserrat',sans-serif;font-size: 15px;\">Access PO</a></p>\n\n\n<p style=\"padding-left: 35px;text-align: justify;line-height: 20px;width: 545px;\">Once you've accepted the PO you can process your shipment. Our operations team will be in touch with you to coordinate invoice submission, ASN updation, and any other assistance you may need. You can contact your POC at <strong><a href=\"mailto:santhosh.n@shakedeal.com\" style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat',sans-serif;color: #2024e8;text-decoration:none;font-size: 10px;\">santhosh.n@shakedeal.com</a></strong> if you have any questions or concerns.</p>\n\n<div style=\"padding-left: 35px\">\n<p style=\"padding-left: 35px;text-align: left;width: 530px;height: 28px;background-color: #fff;color: #0c0c0c;padding: 7px;\">\n <b>Note:</b><span style=\"font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif; font-style:italic\"> The login credentials have already been shared in the initial introduction email of the vendor panel. Kindly refer to that email in case you missed it<span>.\n </p>\n </div>\n <div style=\" display: flex; padding-left: 24px; \">\n \n <a href=\"https://shakedeal.portal.trainn.co/share/14joiwhItlpFJRg1oO8I0A\">\n <img style=\"width: 280px;height: 180px;padding-right: 5px\" alt=\"Hero image\" src=\" https://sdqa.vpanel.shakedeal.com/assets/de8dd34c-20fa-4d67-9f26-dd87c9d4c4fb\" align=\"center\">\n \n </a>\n \n <a href=\"https://shakedeal.portal.trainn.co/share/SZMBJtHWFnC7c4ZcSu1BIQ\">\n <img style=\"width: 280px;height: 178px;padding-right: 79px;\" alt=\"Hero image\" src=\"https://sdqa.vpanel.shakedeal.com/assets/73bd617d-f3a7-4564-abf6-7f271ec3fb62\" align=\"center\">\n </a> \n </div>\n \n <div style=\"padding-bottom: 20px;padding-left: 35px;line-height: 18px; width: 545px;\">\n \n <p style=\" text-align: left; font-size: 10px;\"><strong>Terms and conditions</strong></p>\n <ul style=\"padding-left: 17px\">\n <li style=\" text-align: justify; font-size: 9px;\n \">In rare instances, if you have any concerns with respect to this, please reach out to us immediately.</li>\n <li style=\"text-decoration: none;\n te